{"tid":2107576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局局長楊潤雄：學校需要3日內完成所有考試","createTime":"2020-07-14T03:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T10:04:31.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8f3b46c751822683eadb5495dd03f743ba845b","tid":2107576,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"教育局上周五(10日)宣佈全港中小學、特殊學校及幼稚園由昨日(13日)開始提早放暑假，而重要級別的考試，則可在本星期完成。教育局局長楊潤雄今日（14日）再次向全港學校校長發信，指鑑於本港的疫情在剛過去數天繼續有擴散的跡象，教育局經過通盤考慮下，決定進一步收緊防疫措施，包括學校須在2、3天內完成所有考試、或延後及取消部分考試；另外，學校須由周三（15日）起暫停所有校內活動兩星期，包括所有補課及課外活動，直至本月28日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/FKZYNVKBY3IVX4M7NVWQJWXRLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FFKZYNVKBY3IVX4M7NVWQJWXRLM%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnwVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=b06ee699\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FFKZYNVKBY3IVX4M7NVWQJWXRLM%2F&h=9f25f389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/FKZYNVKBY3IVX4M7NVWQJWXRLM/</a>"},{"pid":"500284cb54fb935bac8594bb89397d19431f6627","tid":2107576,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"點溫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"173f7f9eee67b2c6c217faf674b0184165b5f964","tid":2107576,"uid":264245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:30:29.000Z","msg":"病毒談判成功爭取三日時間"},{"pid":"ba603886a2808bc6796e85e2a2411b9dba2d5978","tid":2107576,"uid":997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"病毒傳心師"},{"pid":"b24d0fa1452ad46bb6deabe828c89e7914ecaddc","tid":2107576,"uid":169819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"公道d講 佢話可以延後既"},{"pid":"c9682a79557dc5646cb68d164